⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Luo Ji
node 3BP · 3BP · ⟦Luo Ji:3BP:e78362⟧

WHO   — Luo Ji — the Wallfacer who understood
WHAT  — The mind that reads the universe's worst secret and weaponizes it: the dark forest's first human master.
WHERE — 3BP · The Three-Body Problem  Framework inputs: Remembrance of Earth's Past (Liu Cixin, 2014-2016) + the Tencent (2023) & Netflix (2024) series; dual-agent web-verified  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the trilogy's central idea needs a discoverer, and Luo Ji is the one who says it out loud and survives.
HOW   — By proving the law (a distant star he names is destroyed), then threatening to broadcast Trisolaris's location if Earth is attacked.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I didn't invent the dark forest. I just looked up and finally understood the rule. Touch us, and I tell the hunters exactly where you live, too.

